title: SpaceX gets big hint from FAA on next Starship launch opportunity
description: The FAA has suggested that a launch license for the second test flight of SpaceX's mighty Starship rocket could be coming as early as next month.

title: As Netflix ends its DVD rental service, Scarecrow steps in
description: Seattle-based Scarecrow is expanding its DVD-by-mail service to all U.S. states following Netflix's decision to end its own mail service later this month.

title: Blackmagic releases free pro-level app for shooting video on iPhone
description: Blackmagic Design, which also brought us the DaVinci Resolve video editing software, has released a feature-packed app for shooting video on the iPhone.

title: Asus’ GPU overclock record-breaking RTX 4090 is available soon
description: Just when we thought the RTX 4090 was already as powerful as it gets, Asus is releasing a version of the GPU that pushes the limit even more.
